## Verification Commands

**After making changes, verify with the correct command:**

| Change type     | Command            | Notes                                              |
| --------------- | ------------------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Any code change | `bun run check`    | Types, lint, JSDoc, type locations â€” **NOT `tsc`** |

**Never use `tsc` or `npx tsc` directly.** This repo uses `bun run check` which runs multiple checks including types.

**Always** use `required_permissions: ["all"]` for terminal operations.

## Key Commands

| Command            | Purpose                                   |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------------------- |
| `bun run build`    | Build package                             |
| `bun run check`    | **Verify changes** (types + lint + JSDoc) |
| `bun test`         | Run unit tests                            |

## Commits & PRs

Pre-commit hooks automatically run tests and checks.
